{"tid":1316132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下次再見到有人冒警的話，即刻打鑊金唔該。","createTime":"2019-07-14T15:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T15:39:42.000Z","uid":112551,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8a108e8261f9e47347fe1f69de1c4ccd4dc8fc21","tid":1316132,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:30:39.000Z","msg":"沒Number無委任證一定係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">冒警</span></span>，因為香港警察係精益求精，全球最守規的紀律部隊，沒可能唔佩戴委任證同唔Show Number。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為市民，希望伸張正義，俾我地再見到 沒Number無委任證 的警察的時候，一定要圍住佢黎打！<br />\n<br />\n死黃屍冒警？下世啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1724c7f2c2dccaf7e9d1a93dc2392b37db609caf","tid":1316132,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:32:23.000Z","msg":"可以阻嚇警察唔敢唔戴證"},{"pid":"42019b666d418262ff199a830b730608e9231783","tid":1316132,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18ea5e9f39fdb550b189fe5dedd012cad049a32a","tid":1316132,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T15:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}